<node CREATED="1580226373182" ID="ID_1973751305" MODIFIED="1580226432199" TEXT="Hot Folders">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <font color="#000000" face="Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Basically the main idea behind hot folders is to transform&#160;</font><font color="rgb(119, 119, 119)" face="Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="15.84px"><strong style="font-weight: normal; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15.84px; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">csv</strong></font><font color="#000000" face="Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&#160;files giving in input to&#160;</font><font color="rgb(119, 119, 119)" face="Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="15.84px"><strong style="font-weight: normal; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15.84px; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">impexes</strong></font><font color="#000000" face="Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&#160;using a pre-configured&#160;</font><code style="font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace; font-size: 14.256px; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 0; color: rgb(189, 65, 71); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font face="Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace" size="2" color="#000000">ImpexConverters</font></code><font color="#000000" face="Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&#160;and import them using&#160;</font><code style="font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace; font-size: 14.256px; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 0; color: rgb(189, 65, 71); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 249); font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font face="Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace" size="2" color="#000000">ImportService</font></code>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node CREATED="1579814813295" ID="ID_153965152" MODIFIED="1579814902534" POSITION="right" TEXT="Flexible Search">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.6; font-family: Open Sans, sans-serif; color: rgb(105, 118, 122); font-style: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      It&#8217;s a hybris&#160;<strong style="font-weight: bold"><b>built-in query language</b></strong>&#160;based on&#160;<strong style="font-weight: bold"><b>SQL syntax</b></strong>.<br />It enables us to&#160;<strong style="font-weight: bold"><b>search</b></strong><b><strong style="font-weight: bold">&#160;</strong></b>the&#160;<strong style="font-weight: bold"><b>records </b></strong>from the&#160;<strong style="font-weight: bold"><b>database</b></strong><b><strong style="font-weight: bold">&#160;</strong></b>using&#160;<strong style="font-weight: bold"><b>item types</b></strong>.<br />In flexible search queries, we&#160;<strong style="font-weight: bold"><b>never</b></strong><b><strong style="font-weight: bold">&#160;</strong></b>use database&#160;<strong style="font-weight: bold"><b>table names</b></strong>.<br />We always use&#160;<strong style="font-weight: bold"><b>item types</b></strong>&#160;which will be&#160;<strong style="font-weight: bold"><b>mapped</b></strong><b><strong style="font-weight: bold">&#160;</strong></b>to a corresponding&#160;<strong style="font-weight: bold"><b>tables</b></strong><b><strong style="font-weight: bold">&#160;</strong></b>by Hybris.
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
